{"word":"ὀξύνω","slug":"ὀξύνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὀξύνω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>ὀξύς</el>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to sharpen</i>: <a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>to goad to anger, provoke</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to sharpen, quicken</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}